<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>غ د ق<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c4">[٣٥٣٦ - غ د ق]</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>غدِقَ يَغدَق، غَدَقًا، فهو غَدِق<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c5">• غدِقتِ الأرضُ:</span><a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>١ - كثُر فيها الماء <span class="c1">"غدِق الوادي"</span> ° غدِق عليه فائضُ نعمتِه.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>٢ - أخصبت.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span class="c5">• غدِق المطرُ:</span> كثُر قَطْرُه وتهطَّل <span class="c1">"تَغدَق الأمطارُ في الشِّتاء"</span>.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span><span class="c5">• غدِقتِ العَيْنُ:</span> فاضت وكثُر ماؤها.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span><span class="c5">⦗١٥٩٨⦘ • غدِقَ العيشُ:</span> غدَق، اتَّسع ورغد <span class="c1">"غدِق عيشُه بعد موسم زراعيّ ناجح"</span>.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>